Citation.sAuthor: Fakhree, M. A. A.[Mohammad A. A.]
Citation.sTitle: Solubility of Anthracene in Binary and Ternary Mixtures of Cyclohexanone, Ethyl Acetate, and Methanol at 298.2 K
Citation.sAbstract: The solubilities of anthracene in binary and ternary mixtures of cyclohexanone + ethyl acetate, cyclohexanone + methanol, ethyl acetate + methanol, and cyclohexanone + ethyl acetate + methanol were reported at 298.2 K. The generated data were fitted to the Jouyban-Acree model, and the overall mean deviation was 5.1 %.
